              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Getting the Job</strong></td>
                <td><span class="cross-icon">✕</span> Sending blind applications and getting filtered out by automated software.</td>
                <td class="accent-column-cell"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Getting your resume fixed by an insider and learning exactly what hiring managers want to hear.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Getting Paid Fairly</strong></td>
