            <p style="font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 500;">*All times shown in Central Time (CT)</p>
            
            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full book-session-btn" id="adv-modal-book-btn" disabled>Schedule</button>
